quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  99,1,When the earth is quaked with its (final) earthquake
  99,2,And the earth brings out its heavy (burdens)
  99,3,"And man says, \"What is it with it"
  99,4,"Upon that Day it will discourse (i.e., proclaim) about its tidings"
  99,5,That your Lord has revealed to it
  99,6,Upon that Day mankind will go forward in diverse (groups) to be shown their deeds
  99,7,So whoever does an atom's weight of charity will see it
  99,8,And whoever does an atom's weight of evil will see it